---
title: San Antonio Beef Bowls with Blue Corn Chips, Fresh Salsa & Lime Crema
description: The beauty of a bowl-style dinner is the DIY element. This meal begins with a base of zesty rice and richly-spiced ground beef, then jazzes things up with homemade salsa, Monterey Jack cheese, a limey crema, and blue corn tortilla chips. When ready to build your bowl, feel free to go wild with assembly. Crema on bottom! Rice on top of chicken! Crush up your tortilla chips for a crunchy garnish, or serve along the side for scooping—follow your heart, chef!!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/san-antonio-beef-bowls-f2975b93.jpg
